{"id":83137,"title":"[Dental care for dependent elderly people].","abstract":"In 1995, the faculty of dental surgery of Paris-Descartes University set up a scheme whereby students at the end of their basic training offer their assistance and skills to institutions caring for dependent elderly people. This article presents a 2011 assessment of the difficulties encountered by the students and nurses' awareness of the importance of integrating oral hygiene into patients' overall care.","date":"2014-01-20","categories":"Stomatognathic Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24437007","annotations":[{"name":"Dentistry","weight":0.722957,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dentistry"},{"name":"Surgery","weight":0.659079,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surgery"},{"name":"Nurse","weight":0.545798,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nurse"},{"name":"Old age","weight":0.336941,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Old_age"},{"name":"Oral hygiene","weight":0.313889,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oral_hygiene"},{"name":"Training","weight":0.305285,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Training"},{"name":"Hygiene","weight":0.16081,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hygiene"},{"name":"Faculty (division)","weight":0.134615,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Faculty_(division)"},{"name":"Recruit training","weight":0.0279596,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Recruit_training"},{"name":"Test (assessment)","weight":0.0197989,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Test_(assessment)"},{"name":"1995","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/1995"},{"name":"Awareness","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Awareness"},{"name":"Dental surgery","weight":0.0157616,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dental_surgery"},{"name":"Mouth","weight":0.0150493